author: Gamers Nexus
description:
Sponsor: Thermal Grizzly Duronaut on Amazon - https://geni.us/tpgcPMw
In this video, we visit JayzTwoCents' studio to check out his hardware testing room, warehouse, and 3D printers. Jay shows us how he's testing GPUs, CPUs, and asks for some advice on setting up new testing methods (that he deployed for the 50-series and that we'll show in the next part of this series). Also, he recently restarted #RIPGN, which means #RIPJAY must return!

Watch our tour of Jay's old office here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=XlfEJwhiMI4
Check out Jay's channel! https://www.youtube.com/jayztwocents
